{"type": "article", "id": 24486, "title": "给鞋子找一个收纳好去处｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。\r\n", "date": "2016-03-26T08:00:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 25415, "name": "鞋架"}, {"id": 25416, "name": "鞋柜"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 500, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071721355tb4LPH8suCUTfcB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<p>挑一款心仪的鞋柜实在太难。想到家里各种长长短短的鞋子，尺寸、格局、外观、材质，与家居环境搭不搭都要考虑。我们本周末的特辑带来一组与鞋子收纳相关的好设计，它们都不是包治百“病”的百搭选择，但各取所需或许能找到一款合适的鞋架或是鞋柜。</p>\n<h2>Zign Shoe Shelf by Zign &amp; Sigurd Larsen </h2>\n<p>德国鞋履品牌 Zign 联手丹麦设计师、建筑师 Sigurd Larsen 设计了一款摩登简约的鞋架，目的不仅是要把你的鞋收放整齐，亦要使其看起来像是“一件艺术品”，既适合当代家居生活空间，亦适于存放现在样式多样的鞋型，多个单元之间可自由组合拼接，灵活性很高。简洁利落的线条和纯净的蓝白配色很搭，Sigurd Larsen 认为自己的这件作品达到了“功能与美学的平衡”。售价 300 欧元，<a href=\"https://zign.com/product/shoe-shelf-white/\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172119gFTOPdjksfMGnal5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.84761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172120qvrPRzZkU5KnVuAY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172120foK7kMs9xhNamJO6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071721210ozJFkeiq6XGMIKL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172121oNaq2cAzMUbCJdTu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172122rVRbxEfS8oYJOADZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>关照鞋柜 by 吱音</h2>\n<p>这是上海原创家居设计品牌吱音推出的关照鞋柜，特别之处在于照鞋镜与全身镜的设计。它的体量并不大，仅适合收纳当季会穿的鞋子。当翻起下半部分的柜门时，则变身照鞋镜；如若把上下柜门都翻开，就成为了全身镜，考虑到了使用者在出门前需要款塑方便搭配衣服和鞋子的需求，实木材质温暖厚实，提供原色与拼色两个版本。售价 1999 元，<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.5-c.w4002-12785662183.90.v5wSoU&amp;id=44738271306\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172122LTkKP9WbhXzEviG2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.488\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172123nexT9HzqshvYJWik.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65466667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172123FwAHJZ9CqdpPI5Mb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.18763326\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172124BgpDLvuqtWVY4UZz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172124sy0EDXoMnr72HQFm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Sko Shoe Rack grey by Normann Copenhagen</h2>\n<p>这款名为“ Sko ”的鞋架是丹麦家居设计品牌 Normann Copenhagen 今年推出的新品，出自当家设计师 Simon Legald 之手。Sko 省去了一切不必要的组件，一个木质框架加两片穿孔钢板用螺丝固定即可，典型的斯堪的纳维亚风格。正是因为它的简单，所以很百搭，既适合放在门厅入口处也适合置于卧室内，纯白与深灰两种颜色都是很低调的选择。售价 265 美元，<a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/products/sko-shoe-rack?v=601065\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172124y1RIPUMBk7GbEic9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172125AQCJg98cbtiEqmvM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172125kdvhp5GxNzEbYlCQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071721262AnzY6Ti0D97p5cy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<p>          </p>\n<h2>ShoeTrap</h2>\n<p>这款鞋柜是一个一个独立的方盒子，朝向最外面是玻璃门，可以上下或左右拉开。盒子排列在一起后其边缘得以加粗，非常复古。每一双鞋装在一个盒子里，有三种型号，可以顺着墙面搭配出想要的高度，体现出更强的灵活性。它不会让你的鞋柜显得空，而当你有太多的鞋子时又可以在另外一面墙上堆出一个柜子。鞋柜有红木、樱桃木和枫木三种材料选择，<a href=\"http://www.shoetrap.com/products.asp\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071721272nKUApfXj6gB4rEu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.29454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172127KTV05RAu2mFWHdO3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77272727\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071721281iN3a98wOBA5dmJD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77272727\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172128wnDjYr02UzcOtlpg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77272727\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172129CMSzl6Gw8s1RNIT2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6275\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>MIXED-USE STORAGE UNITS by Sebastian Erazo Fischer</h2>\n<p>这是一款专门放在玄关的鞋柜，它结合了挂衣服、坐着换鞋等多个功能。它用浅色的枫木条制作，每一条之间都留有缝隙，像是在公园里摆放的长椅，营造一种轻松的户外气氛。在缝隙之间插上了一些小的木块作为挂钩，随手挂上脱下的衣服，很方便。它另有一款不带横排座位的，可以节约更多空间。<a href=\"http://www.sebastianerazo.com/shoe-coat-shelfbench\">点击这里可以查看详细信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172129ZCmHQyuFKtONe4JY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172130DfPMCOitqnv5NV3y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172130w5BgrkHOQZWKpYlq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172131n0iKvgZU6Q8JdoS4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172131pezHsyQR6XEZUYNh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>          </p>\n<h2>定制的鞋柜</h2>\n<p>这整面墙都是鞋柜，它实际上是将不同的格子、木板等最基本的元素搭配在一起而拼凑出来的，像是一个更衣室。可以看到在中间有三个木质吊柜，围绕着它有不少白色的木板作为衔接，相互错落又保持了整体的整洁，也是灵活可变的方式。看起来很简单，但也许是最适合的收纳。<a href=\"http://www.leroymerlin.fr/big/guides-2015/guide-maison-n2/index.html?xtor=EPR-600002805\">这是它们的网站</a>，还提供定制设计。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071721327M5pOxyDoPNc9FeA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98491379\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172132iroIHBJsR1cuFk5L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68611111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172133dzxiDeYfh3k5OwLX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071721331kfjxVyrzoJqEhlW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607172134w7ZjygmlGSCn4vkT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071721344eYjNvtW2qJTnbQi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://zign.com/product/shoe-shelf-white/\">Zign</a>、<a href=\"https://item.taobao.com/item.htm?spm=a1z10.5-c.w4002-12785662183.90.v5wSoU&amp;id=44738271306\">吱音</a>、<a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/products/sko-shoe-rack?v=601065\">Normann Copenhagen</a>、<a href=\"http://www.shoetrap.com/products.asp\">ShoeTrap</a>、<a href=\"http://www.sebastianerazo.com/shoe-coat-shelfbench\">Sebastian Erazo Fischer</a></p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n\n\n"}